[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0247","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0247.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0108","title":"SGI IRIX 6.3 xrm 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 操作系统的 printers 程序中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xrm 组件提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞仅需本地用户权限即可利用，影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0108"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.280","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.4 及以上版本，或安装 SGI 提供的补丁程序。作为临时缓解措施，限制对受影响系统的本地访问权限，仅授权可信用户使用，并移除 setuid 权限位。鉴于 IRIX 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/bugtraq/1997/May/191","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19267","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0108","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0108.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83064/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0828884e-fed7-43ba-9578-192236803d75.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0247.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0398","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0398.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0212","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.mountd 错误信息泄露漏洞","description":"Solaris/SunOS 系统中 RPC 服务 rpc.mountd 存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该服务返回详细错误信息，从而枚举服务器上的文件系统结构和文件是否存在。该漏洞影响 Solaris 及 SunOS 多个版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，为后续攻击收集目标信息。官方已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0212"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.403","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin #168 (1998年发布) 对应的操作系统补丁，更新至已修复该问题的 Solaris 版本。如无法打补丁，可在 /etc/hosts.deny 中添加 \"mountd: ALL\" 并用 /etc/hosts.allow 按需放行可信主机，同时在防火墙上限制对 rpc.mountd (端口 2049 及 rpcbind 端口 111) 的访问。若不需要 NFS 服务，可停止并禁用 mountd 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/168","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-048.shtml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0398.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0170","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0170.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0069","title":"Sun Solaris ufsdump/ufsrestore 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 ufsdump/ufsrestore 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过向该工具传递特制参数触发溢出，覆盖内存数据，进而实现权限提升或以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高危，需系统本地账号方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0069"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.363","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至 Solaris 8 及以上版本，或安装 Sun 官方补丁 106880-01 (SPARC) / 106881-01 (x86)。临时缓解措施：限制 ufsdump/ufsrestore 的 setuid 权限，仅授权管理用户执行文件系统备份操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/169","http://www.osvdb.org/8158","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19534","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0069","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f06304a9243ce013bfbf7cea427539f6409c0a05/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0069.md","https://github.com/krafthack-by-techday/Night-s-watch/blob/30ae1bcc335306fe4c5507b2c629cae4932e515e/cve/nvd/CVE-1999-0069_0f0c3530-7572-4860-a943-991d78115c24","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqg2-r5rv-62x6/GHSA-xqg2-r5rv-62x6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0170.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0170.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0170.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1261","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1261.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1390","title":"Debian suidmanager 0.18 命令执行漏洞","description":"Debian suidmanager 0.18 版本中的 suidexec 组件存在命令执行漏洞。当系统安装此版本时，只要存在任意一条 suid root 的 shell 脚本，本地攻击者即可通过调用 /usr/bin/suidexec 指定恶意程序和目标脚本路径，以 root 权限执行任意命令，从而导致本地提权至 root。攻击需具备本地用户权限且系统已安装受影响版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1390"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 suidmanager 至 >=0.19 版本或使用 sudo 替代工具管理特权提升。Debian 官方已发布安全公告 DSA-006-1，提供补丁和修复方案。安装最新 Debian 更新包以修复此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1390","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/94","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19080"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19080"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1261.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1236","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1236.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1113","title":"Qualcomm Eudora Internet Mail Server 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Qualcomm Eudora Internet Mail Server (EIMS) 2.01 及更早版本在 MacOS 系统上存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 106 端口发送超长的 USER 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 EIMS 2.01 及之前版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，利用难度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1113"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.867","remediation":"受影响版本为 Eudora Internet Mail Server 2.01 及更早版本。该产品已停止维护多年，建议迁移至现代邮件服务器（如 Postfix、Microsoft Exchange、Cyrus IMAP）。若因老系统兼容性无法迁移，应在防火墙层面限制对 TCP 端口 106 的访问，只允许可信 IP 连接，以降低被远程利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=89258194718577&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/75","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19069","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1113.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1113","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1113.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1113.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f3c5-443m-3w9q/GHSA-f3c5-443m-3w9q.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/poppassd_too_long_user.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/75/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1113.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9f9f8904-8bd2-49ab-807a-504523f0e837.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/0b7b3d855cd8fca7b800fb29d6754e2da82897b6/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1236.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1290","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1290.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1499","title":"ISC BIND named 符号链接本地文件破坏漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 4.9 和 8.1 版本的 named 进程存在符号链接竞争条件漏洞。本地攻击者可在 named 进程以 root 权限运行时，通过预先创建指向敏感系统文件的符号链接（named_dump.db 或 named.stats），诱导 root 进程在接收 SIGINT 或 SIGIOT 信号转储调试文件时跟随符号链接覆盖任意关键文件，导致任意文件破坏。该漏洞影响 ISC BIND 4.9 和 8.1 版本，攻击条件为本地用户权限且需诱导 root 进程发送特定信号，利用方式为符号链接竞争条件攻击导致任意文件覆盖破坏，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1499"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:34.333","remediation":"建议升级到 ISC BIND 4.9.8 或 8.1.1 及以上版本修复该符号链接漏洞。若暂无法升级，请以非 root 权限运行 named 进程并配置 chroot 监狱限制文件系统访问，防止 root 进程被信号杀死时触发符号链接攻击破坏文件系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/8966","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/80","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19072","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe9e77bf3808998cc7ef33bc8a5ea311f35fadb0/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1499.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1499","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1499.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1499.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wg36-cvm4-gq96/GHSA-wg36-cvm4-gq96.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1499.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b1e34665-48e9-4d98-9441-a8fe2dd9ea27.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1290.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1290.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1290.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1291","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1291.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1504","title":"Stalker Internet Mail Server 1.6 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Stalker Internet Mail Server 1.6 存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 SMTP 服务发送超长的 HELO 命令触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务拒绝服务（崩溃）。该漏洞影响 Stalker Internet Mail Server 1.6 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发起攻击，CVSS 评分 5.0（中等危害），主要导致拒绝服务而非代码执行。该漏洞发布于 1999 年，相关产品早已停止维护，建议升级至新版邮件服务器或迁移至现代邮件解决方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1504"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:34.980","remediation":"建议立即停用 Stalker Internet Mail Server 1.6 并迁移至现代维护中的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix、Exim、Exchange 等）。若必须暂时保留，请在防火墙层面限制 SMTP 端口(25/587)仅允许可信 IP 访问，并在 SMTP 代理/网关层面限制 HELO/EHLO 命令长度不超过 255 字符，同时配置 SMTP 服务拒绝过长 HELO 命令作为临时缓解措施。建议尽快迁移替代，该软件已停止维护多年无官方补丁。要求升级到现代邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix 3.x、Exchange 2019+），并在边界防火墙限制 SMTP 端口仅对受信 IP 开放，同时在邮件网关配置 HELO 命令长度限制（≤255 字符）作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/8951","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/62","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19047","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d08a5c34806fec51f3d6c8b496ad617d8294f215/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1504.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1504","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1504.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1504.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qjcj-gc7c-j4r2/GHSA-qjcj-gc7c-j4r2.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/smtp_helo.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1504.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/62/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1291.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1238","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1238.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1114","title":"SGI IRIX Korn Shell suid_exec 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IRIX 6.4 及更早版本中 Korn Shell (ksh) 的 suid_exec 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该 setuid 程序传入特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.x 及更早版本操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1114"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.003","remediation":"SGI 已于 1999 年发布 IRIX 6.5 及后续安全补丁修复此漏洞，建议立即升级至 IRIX 6.5.22 及以上版本。如无法升级，可通过 `chmod 4555 /usr/lib/ksh/suid_exec` 移除 suid_exec 的 setuid 位，禁止普通用户以 root 权限执行该程序，作为临时缓解措施。对于仍在运行 IRIX 的系统，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-15a.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/467","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2100","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19353","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1114.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1114","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1114.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1114.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-fjg7-227f-7rfj/GHSA-fjg7-227f-7rfj.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000282.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2b2febe6-40dd-4e6a-9b8a-57d63e732aa3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1114.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1238.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1227","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1227.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1015","title":"Apple AppleShare IP Mail Server 远程拒绝服务缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Apple 公司出品的 AppleShare IP Mail Server 5.0.3（运行于 MacOS 8.1 及更早版本）的 SMTP 服务在处理客户端命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该服务在解析 HELO 命令时未对输入长度做有效边界校验，当远程攻击者向目标邮件服务器发送超出预期长度的超长 HELO 命令参数时，会导致缓冲区溢出并使服务进程崩溃，从而引发拒绝服务（DoS）。攻击无需身份认证，只要攻击者可网络访问目标服务器的 SMTP 端口即可发起，影响范围为部署了上述版本 AppleShare Mail Server 的 MacOS 8.1 及更早系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1015"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.597","remediation":"立即将 AppleShare IP Mail Server 升级至 Apple 后续发布的修复版本（建议升级到 Mac OS 9 配套的 AppleShare IP 6.x 或更新的 Mail Server 组件）。在无法立即升级的情况下，应在边界防火墙或邮件网关上限制仅允许可信内网 IP 访问 25 端口的 SMTP 服务，丢弃超长 HELO 命令请求，并部署入侵检测规则拦截异常长度的 SMTP 命令作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=89200657216213&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/61","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19046","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1015.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1015","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1015.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1015.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q25m-8j2c-m6fp/GHSA-q25m-8j2c-m6fp.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/smtp_helo.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1015.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000280.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f8d04726-d7a9-4b2c-bcd5-81b99b896744.json","https://github.com/D14b0l1c/vulnerability-analyzer/blob/f6e8040ce803e0ca2c5b05b240848cd14c1adfab/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1227.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0373","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0373.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0190","title":"Sun Solaris rpcbind 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 rpcbind 服务存在任意文件写入漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 rpcbind 服务发送特制 RPC 请求，利用符号链接或文件路径遍历等方式覆盖系统任意文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议及时安装对应安全补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0190"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:49.320","remediation":"立即应用 Sun Security Bulletin #167 提供的补丁程序，或升级到 Solaris 7 及以上版本。作为临时缓解措施，在 /etc/hosts.deny 中添加 ALL:ALL 限制 rpcbind 访问，并在防火墙上仅允许受信任网络访问 rpcbind 端口 111/TCP 和 111/UDP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/167"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0373.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0046","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0011","title":"ISC BIND 4.9/8 CNAME及区域传输拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 4.9 和 BIND 8 版本的域名解析服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者通过发送特制的 CNAME 资源记录或利用不规范的区域传输（Zone Transfer）请求，可导致目标 BIND 服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，停止响应正常的域名解析请求。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 DNS 服务器，在无需认证的条件下即可触发，对网络基础设施的可用性构成直接威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0011"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.490","remediation":"立即升级 ISC BIND 至 8.2 及以上版本，推荐直接迁移至 BIND 9.x 系列。在 named.conf 中配置 allow-transfer 仅允许受信从服务器（如 allow-transfer { 192.168.1.2; };），并在面向不可信网络的接口上通过 allow-query 和 allow-recursion 限制查询来源。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙阻断外部对 TCP 53 端口的区域传输请求，并限制 UDP 53 的异常 CNAME 查询流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/180","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0046.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0044","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0010","title":"ISC BIND 4.9/8 DNS Message 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 4.9 及 8 版本中的 DNS 消息处理组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的恶意 DNS 查询消息，利用消息解析过程中的缺陷触发服务崩溃，导致 DNS 服务不可用。该漏洞影响大量使用上述版本 BIND 的 DNS 服务器，攻击者通过发送精心构造的 DNS 请求报文即可实施攻击，无需复杂前置条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0010"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.340","remediation":"升级至 BIND 8.2 或更高版本以修复 DNS 消息解析缺陷；BIND 4.9/8 系列已停止维护，建议迁移至 BIND 9.x 系列并升级到 ISC 发布的最新稳定版（如 9.18.x 或 9.20.x）。如暂无法升级，应在边界防火墙上限制外部 DNS 查询来源 IP 并启用递归查询访问控制列表以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0030","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0009","title":"ISC BIND 反向查询远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC BIND（Berkeley Internet Name Domain）4.9 及 8.x 版本存在反向查询缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 DNS 服务器发送特制的反向查询请求，触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响运行 BIND 4.9 及 8.x 的多种操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商建议立即升级至不受影响的版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0009"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.137","remediation":"立即升级 BIND 至 8.2 或更高版本，或在条件允许时迁移至 BIND 9 系列（如 9.3.0+），因为 8.2 已修复逆查询缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在 named.conf 中禁用 `inverse-query` 选项以临时缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/180","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/134","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19112","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0009","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0009.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/252.txt","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/710308a4be78e89bc993b4d594b444aeb805b7d8/Packs/McAfeeNSM/Integrations/McAfeeNSMv2/README.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-p4fw-6pfr-4xqr/GHSA-p4fw-6pfr-4xqr.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/deleted.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bind_iquery.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1298","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1298.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1040","title":"SGI IRIX NetWare Client ipxchk/ipxlink 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 和 6.4 系统上 NetWare Client 1.0 的 ipxchk 与 ipxlink 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。攻击者可通过修改 IFS 环境变量，使这两个程序以 root 权限执行任意命令，从而完全控制系统。该漏洞仅需本地登录账号即可利用，无需远程访问权限，可导致攻击者获取系统最高权限，严重威胁系统机密性、完整性和可用性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1040"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-04-08","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 SGI 安全补丁 Advisory 19980501-01-P2869，将 NetWare Client 升级至修复版本；或从系统中移除 ipxchk 与 ipxlink 程序。同时应限制本地用户对 IFS 环境变量的写入权限，避免漏洞被利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-055.shtml","https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=89217373930054&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/082f2f7e857643469b13565b89f2acba96998d2e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1040.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1298.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1288","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1288.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1498","title":"Slackware Linux pkgtool 本地符号链接临时文件读写漏洞","description":"Slackware Linux 3.4 系统自带的 pkgtool 软件包管理工具在运行过程中会创建并读写临时应答文件（reply file），但其未对临时文件路径进行安全的创建与校验。本地已登录的普通用户可通过预先创建指向任意系统文件的符号链接（symlink attack），使 pkgtool 在后续操作中误将攻击者指定的链接目标当作临时文件进行读取或写入。该漏洞影响运行 Slackware Linux 3.4 并可使用 pkgtool 的本地用户，攻击条件为攻击者在目标系统拥有本地账户且能操纵临时目录。成功利用后，攻击者可将自身权限提升至文件所有者权限，读取敏感配置文件或覆写系统关键文件（如密码文件、启动脚本），进而造成信息泄露或本地权限提升。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1498"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:34.210","remediation":"建议立即将 Slackware Linux 升级至 3.6 或更高版本，该版本已在 hdsetup.tgz 包中对 pkgtool 等包管理工具的 /tmp 临时文件符号链接攻击进行了修复。如暂无法升级，可在运行系统上执行 installpkg hdsetup.tgz 应用补丁，并以 root 用户执行 touch /tmp/PKGTOOL.REMOVED 创建临时文件阻止符号链接利用，同时将 /tmp 目录权限设置为 1777 以限制普通用户创建符号链接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/82","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19074","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe9e77bf3808998cc7ef33bc8a5ea311f35fadb0/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1498.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1498","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1498.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1498.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r9wh-3q4r-xc56/GHSA-r9wh-3q4r-xc56.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1498.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000277.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--258e7ca7-f067-4731-acf0-558f8b5ff87e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1288.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1288.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1288.toml"}]